These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, tea, juice, almond-milk
4 different pets are kept: lizard, hamster, chinchilla, hedgehog
There are 4 different nationalities: canadian, colombian, indonesian, polish
The people use 4 different means of transport: bus, jet-ski, tram, trike
1. the colombian is the owner of the hedgehog##1
2. the indonesian is between the person drinking juice and the person drinking almond-milk##2
3. the colombian is the person driving the bus##1
4. the person driving the trike is on the left of the person driving the bus##1
5. the owner of the lizard is on the left of the canadian##1
6. the person driving the tram is the person drinking juice##1
7. the owner of the hamster is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
8. the canadian is on the far right##1
9. the person drinking tea is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3      |    4     |
| Beverage   | tea | almond-milk   | iced-tea  | juice  |
| Pet   | hamster    | hedgehog    | lizard      | chinchilla    |
| Nationality   | polish | colombian | indonesian | canadian |
| Transport     | trike  | bus       | jet-ski    | tram     |

