.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-2::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: cooking, drawing, singing, woodworking
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: action, adventure, scientific, western
There are 4 different nationalities: american, french, canadian, polish
The people have 4 different jobs:  manager, project-manager, videographer, pilot
1. the pilot is on the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
2. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the far right##1
3. the polish is the project-manager##1
4. the person who's hobby is singing is on the right of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
5. the person watching western movies is between the canadian and the manager##2
6. the pilot is between the person watching western movies and the polish##2
7. the american is on the far right##1
8. the person watching adventure movies is on the left of the person who's hobby is singing##1
9. the person watching scientific movies is on the right of the french##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3     |     4      |
| Hobby         | woodworking | drawing    | singing  | cooking    |
| Movie-Genre   | action      | adventure  | western  | scientific |
| Nationality           | polish      | canadian       | french      | american       |
| Job         | project-manager    | pilot | videographer | manager |

