.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-3::.
There 4 different types of food: artichoke, blueberry, lemon, mango
The people have 4 different hobbies: camping, fishing, photography, traveling
House: tower, futuristic, craftsman, victorian
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: skiing, basketball, climbing, biathlon
1. the craftsman house is the person who's sport is basketball##1
2. the person who's sport is basketball is on the left of the victorian house##1
3. the person who's sport is climbing is on the left of the person who's sport is basketball##1
4. the person who's sport is basketball is on the left of the person who's sport is skiing##1
5. the person eating lemon is on the left of the person who's hobby is photography##1
6. the futuristic house is the person who's hobby is traveling##1
7. the person eating mango is on the right of the person who's hobby is photography##1
8. the person eating artichoke is between the person who's hobby is camping and the person who's hobby is traveling##2
9. the person who's hobby is photography is between the person eating lemon and the futuristic house##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |     2     |      3      |     4     |
| Food        | blueberry | lemon     | artichoke   | mango     |
| Hobby       | fishing   | camping   | photography | traveling |
| House         | tower   | craftsman | victorian       | futuristic    |
| Sport   | climbing    | basketball | skiing  | biathlon    |

