.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-4::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  fisherman, mechanic, police-officer, teacher
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: action, disaster, martial-arts, scientific
There 4 different types of food: banana, cherry, pumpkin, strawberry
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: azalea, orchid, amaryllis, bellflower
 1. the person watching disaster movies is on the far right##1
 2. the person watching scientific movies is the fisherman##1
 3. the person eating banana is on the right of the person who growsbellflower##1
 4. the person who growsazalea is on the far left##1
 5. the person watching scientific movies is the person eating cherry##1
 6. the person eating strawberry is on the right of the person who growsazalea##1
 7. the person watching disaster movies is the police-officer##1
 8. the person watching action movies is on the right of the person watching scientific movies##1
 9. the fisherman is on the left of the person who growsorchid##1
10. the mechanic is between the person eating banana and the teacher##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |      3       |       4        |
| Job           | fisherman  | teacher | mechanic     | police-officer |
| Movie-Genre   | scientific | action  | martial-arts | disaster       |
| Food           | cherry       | strawberry    | pumpkin      | banana           |
| Flower         | azalea | orchid   | bellflower   | amaryllis         |

