.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-5::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: fantaade, 7up, fanta, soy-milk
The people have 4 different jobs:  freelancer, lawyer, security-guard, social-worker
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: adventure, epic, romance, scientific
The people have 4 different hobbies: collecting, baking, video-games, camping
 1. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1
 2. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the far left##1
 3. the security-guard is the person drinking 7up##1
 4. the security-guard is on the left of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
 5. the person watching scientific movies is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1
 6. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the person watching scientific movies##1
 7. the social-worker is on the left of the person drinking fantaade##1
 8. the lawyer is the person watching epic movies##1
 9. the person drinking fanta is between the person who's hobby is camping and the person watching adventure movies##2
10. the person watching romance movies is the person who's hobby is video-games##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |       2       |       3       |     4      |
| Beverage          | 7up         | fanta         | fantaade     | soy-milk      |
| Job           | security-guard | social-worker | freelancer    | lawyer     |
| Movie-Genre   | adventure      | romance       | scientific    | epic       |
| Hobby         | collecting     | video-games       | camping | baking |

