.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-6::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: rose, balloon-flower, daisy, begonia
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: folk, funk, jazz, punk
There are 4 different nationalities: chinese, dutch, polish, turkish
The people use 4 different means of transport: van, jet-ski, bus, car
1. the fan of folk is between the person driving the car and the fan of jazz##2
2. the person who growsballoon-flower is between the fan of folk and the turkish##2
3. the polish is between the person driving the jet-ski and the dutch##2
4. the person who growsdaisy is on the left of the dutch##1
5. the polish is the polish##1
6. the dutch is on the right of the person driving the bus##1
7. the dutch is on the left of the person who growsrose##1
8. the fan of jazz is on the far right##1
9. the fan of funk is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3     |     4     |
| Flower           | daisy | balloon-flower | rose  | begonia |
| Music-Genre   | funk      | punk       | folk     | jazz      |
| Nationality   | turkish   | dutch      | polish   | chinese   |
| Transport         | bus   | car    | van | jet-ski   |

