.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-7::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: family, fantasy, time-travel, zombie
House: townhouse, cottage, tower, craftsman
There are 4 different nationalities: argentine, british, dutch, russian
There are 4 different favourite beverages: fanta, iced-tea, coffee, 7up
 1. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the townhouse house##1
 2. the person watching fantasy movies is the dutch##1
 3. the cottage house is between the dutch and the person drinking coffee##2
 4. the tower house is the person drinking 7up##1
 5. the russian is on the left of the person watching zombie movies##1
 6. the person watching fantasy movies is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
 7. the argentine is the person drinking fanta##1
 8. the craftsman house is on the far right##1
 9. the person watching fantasy movies is on the right of the person watching time-travel movies##1
10. the dutch is the person drinking 7up##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Movie-Genre   | time-travel | fantasy | family  | zombie  |
| House   | townhouse       | tower   | cottage | craftsman    |
| Nationality   | argentine   | dutch   | russian | british |
| Beverage     | fanta    | 7up   | iced-tea    | coffee  |

