.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-8::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  project-manager, scientist, dressmaker, musician
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: documentary, drama, satire, zombie
4 different pets are kept: cat, frog, horse, snake
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: weightlifting, soccer, water-polo, snowboarding
1. the person watching drama movies is between the person who's sport is water-polo and the person who's sport is weightlifting##2
2. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the left of the musician##1
3. the owner of the cat is on the left of the owner of the horse##1
4. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the left of the scientist##1
5. the person who's sport is soccer is between the person who's sport is water-polo and the person watching documentary movies##2
6. the dressmaker is the person watching zombie movies##1
7. the musician is on the left of the owner of the frog##1
8. the project-manager is on the left of the scientist##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |      3      |   4    |
| Job      | dressmaker  | musician   | project-manager    | scientist  |
| Movie-Genre   | zombie    | drama   | documentary | satire |
| Pet           | cat       | horse   | frog        | snake  |
| Sport     | water-polo | soccer | weightlifting         | snowboarding |

