.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-9::.
There 4 different types of food: grapefruit, lettuce, spinach, tomato
The people have 4 different jobs:  accountant, designer, fisherman, social-worker
The people use 4 different means of transport: roller, trike, subway, boat
House: townhouse, wooden, futuristic, craftsman
 1. the person eating lettuce is the fisherman##1
 2. the person eating tomato is the futuristic house##1
 3. the fisherman is the wooden house##1
 4. the person eating spinach is on the right of the person eating tomato##1
 5. the person driving the boat is the person eating grapefruit##1
 6. the person driving the subway is on the far left##1
 7. the designer is on the left of the fisherman##1
 8. the person driving the trike is on the far right##1
 9. the accountant is between the social-worker and the townhouse house##2
10. the person eating tomato is on the left of the person eating spinach##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |     3      |     4     |
| Food          | tomato        | spinach    | grapefruit | lettuce   |
| Job           | social-worker | accountant | designer   | fisherman |
| Transport   | subway         | roller       | boat      | trike     |
| House         | futuristic       | craftsman | townhouse    | wooden  |

