.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-10::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, lemonade, mirinda, sprite
There 4 different types of food: corn, nectarine, onion, plum
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: martial-arts, scientific, mystery, adventure
City: london, prague, marseilles, hannover
 1. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1
 2. the person traveling to london is on the right of the person traveling to marseilles##1
 3. the person watching scientific movies is on the right of the person watching adventure movies##1
 4. the person eating corn is the person drinking lemonade##1
 5. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1
 6. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the right of the person eating corn##1
 7. the person traveling to marseilles is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
 8. the person traveling to hannover is between the person eating corn and the person eating onion##2
 9. the person eating plum is on the right of the person traveling to prague##1
10. the person watching martial-arts movies is between the person eating corn and the person eating onion##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |     2      |      3      |       4       |
| Beverage   | lemonade    | mirinda    | sprite      | hot-chocolate |
| Food       | corn        | plum       | onion       | nectarine     |
| Movie-Genre      | mystery | martial-arts | adventure | scientific        |
| City        | prague       | hannover     | marseilles         | london           |

