City: boston, nizza, san-francisco, liverpool
The people have 4 different hobbies: board-games, traveling, writing, drawing
The people use 4 different means of transport: jet-ski, subway, train, van
 1. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the right of the person driving the train##1
 2. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the left of the person driving the jet-ski##1
 3. the person eating kale is on the right of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
 4. the person traveling to nizza is on the right of the person eating cherry##1
 5. the person traveling to nizza is between the person traveling to boston and the person traveling to liverpool##2
 6. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left of the person who's hobby is writing##1
 7. the person who's hobby is drawing is the person eating cucumber##1
 8. the person driving the van is on the far right##1
 9. the person traveling to liverpool is the person driving the train##1
10. the person who's hobby is board-games is the person eating kale##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |    2     |    3     |     4      |
| Food        | cherry  | cucumber | kale     | carrot     |
| City         | liverpool | nizza | boston     | san-francisco |
| Hobby       | traveling  | drawing   | board-games | writing    |
| Transport   | train   | subway   | jet-ski  | van        |

