4. the fan of punk is on the left of the person playing monopoly##1
5. the owner of the dog is between the owner of the ferret and the fan of indie##2
6. the fan of gospel is the owner of the bird##1
7. the person watching animation movies is the person playing billiard##1
8. the fan of gospel is the person playing canasta##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |     3      |     4     |
| Music-Genre         | indie   | punk  | r&b | gospel   |
| Movie-Genre   | animation | documentary | zombie     | adventure |
| Pet           | snake     | dog         | ferret     | bird      |
| Game         | billiard    | go  | monopoly     | canasta   |

