4. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the left of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
5. the fan of classical is the person who's sport is climbing##1
6. the fan of funk is on the left of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
7. the musician is on the right of the fan of classical##1
