4. the person who's birthday is in october is the person eating nectarine##1
5. the japanese is on the far left##1
6. the person eating nectarine is on the right of the person driving the car##1
7. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left of the person who's birthday is in june##1
8. the thai is on the right of the person eating pepper##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |     3      |     4     |
